{"tid":54501,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【王者君臨】 看似會援交的動畫角色排行2016","createTime":"2016-12-25T14:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T05:01:50.000Z","uid":34037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87748170b095589ed5b04f2a70455ce8e0e58e30","tid":54501,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"【王者君臨】「看似會援交的動畫角色排行2016」 Top1連續五年稱霸，王者地位無人可撼動！！！<br />\n<br />\n之前8月時在日本2ch上慣例的看似會援交的動畫角色排行公開，由東山奈央配音的新子憧已經連續五年在這個排行榜上稱霸<br />\n而且在前十的角色中也有不少是東山奈央配音的，以至於這個排行榜現在第一已經固定化，在平安夜的時候視頻版也已經出爐，除了前十外還可以看到更多角色在榜單上的排行<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm30290412?via=thumb_watch&amp;at=title&amp;state=unplayed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nicovideo.jp%2Fwatch%2Fsm30290412%3Fvia%3Dthumb_watch%26at%3Dtitle%26state%3Dunplayed&d=Ttds0xcXRO%2BjCWok1iePRZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c20e35ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm30290412?via=thumb_watch&amp;at=title&amp;state=unplayed</a><br />\n第 10 位：西川葉子 CV：和久井優<br />\n<img src=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F10-6.jpg&h=e23571a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第 9 位：川神舞 CV：上坂堇<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/09-6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F09-6.jpg&d=Ttds0xcXRO%2BjCWok1iePRZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=ee0d9743\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/09-6.jpg</a><br />\n第 8 位：青羽心夏 CV：小倉唯<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/08-6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F08-6.jpg&d=Ttds0xcXRO%2BjCWok1iePRZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cc0e2453\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/08-6.jpg</a><br />\n第 6 位：九條可憐 CV：東山奈央<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/07-6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F07-6.jpg&d=Ttds0xcXRO%2BjCWok1iePRZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e968a3e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/07-6.jpg</a><br />\n第 6 位：由比濱結衣 CV：東山奈央<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/06-6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F06-6.jpg&d=Ttds0xcXRO%2BjCWok1iePRZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cb6b10f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/06-6.jpg</a><br />\n第 5 位：一色彩羽 CV：佐倉綾音<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/05-8.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F05-8.jpg&d=Ttds0xcXRO%2BjCWok1iePRZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=30eaec8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/05-8.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"5551843aff3d629075b983638010bc8e793b38f4","tid":54501,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:07:55.000Z","msg":"個榜不如索性叫「東山今年配過咩角色」算啦？"},{"pid":"c24022086dcb5f208d6b8bc5b30288be1428574a","tid":54501,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"新田下海<br />\n名義排第二，實質第一"},{"pid":"02f15f0d1f2a66eb5fffc70d5e4e2bb57b1efa15","tid":54501,"uid":7778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新田下海<br />\n名義排第二，實質第一</blockquote><br />\n反正新子憧點都係第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc3a1e6288f2f926382447774232ac7e0dbd958","tid":54501,"uid":59878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"8月咪出左old nees<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a7394e64d9d76846ab035d4ed12af20d740573","tid":54501,"uid":26506,"l